text_complet = "Life in our village has always been peaceful, until this morning. While exploring the edge of the forest, the ground collapsed beneath my feet, revealing a bottomless pit that seems to breathe a cold air from long ago.\n\nThey say whoever falls into it never returns... or at least not empty-handed. I feel a strange force pulling me towards the darkness. It’s not just a hole; it’s a gateway to something forgotten. If I can find the 5 gold coins mentioned in the legends, maybe I will activate the portal that brings me back to the light.\n\nI take a deep breath. The adventure begins with a single step into the unknown.";

